# Copy this file to `native/.env` and fill in the value, then restart Expo with `-c`.
# These are PUBLIC client values (the anon key already ships in the web bundle).
#
# Supabase dashboard → Settings → API:
#   - "Project URL"  → EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL   (optional; defaults to the live project)
#   - "anon public"  → EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY  (required)

